process

public void process(Interest interest)
Parse incoming interests for type and dispatch those dedicated to some special purpose. Interests can be to start a write or a name enumeration request. If the interest has no special purpose, its assumed that it's to actually read data from the repository and the request is sent to the RepositoryStore to be processed.
